com.sun.enterprise.tools.verifier.hk2

Class PackageAnalyser.SplitPackage

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sun.enterprise.tools.verifier.hk2.PackageAnalyser.SplitPackage
  • Enclosing class:
    PackageAnalyser

    public static class PackageAnalyser.SplitPackage
extends Object
    Holds information about a split-package. A split-package is a package whose contents come from multiple bundles. Note that, a package can be exported by multiple bundles. It leads to problematic scenarios when the symmetric difference of set of classes for a package from the two bundles is not an empty set. In other words, they should contain identical set of classes from the same package.
